item.description:
Definition of and configuration for an auto-update channel.
Used by: &lt;manifest&gt;
Blocks Block Description darwin { … } Darwin-specific configuration. linux { … } Linux-specific configuration. on &lt;event&gt; { … } Triggers to run on lifecycle events. platform &lt;attr&gt; { … } Platform-specific configuration. &lt;attr&gt; is a set regexes that must all match against one of CPU, OS, etc.

